{"title":"实现一个前后端的友链兼留言板小项目","uid":"641f672b78debb460796f7a65a68b01a","slug":"friend-link","date":"2022-12-20T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-27T12:07:31.030Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/friend-link.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/cover.jpg","content":"<p>因为现在使用的主题仍处于开发和Bug比较多的阶段，没有提供友链页面，所以这部分自然而然就需要自己完成了。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>主题作者跑路又是另一回事了。</p></blockquote>\n<p>首先是技术选型，即怎么写自己最舒服，同时还要考虑怎么部署最便宜。</p>\n<p>因为友链这一部分的变动比较频繁，所以使用前后端的模式是比较合适的。前端自然就选用我最熟悉的<strong>Vue3</strong>；而后端因为我想去服务器化，所以就只有选用<strong>nodejs</strong>了，然后将后端的接口服务部署到<strong>vercel</strong>上。</p>\n<p>至于数据库，因为这个项目的后端本来就很小，所以就不需要了，直接读取<code>.json</code>文件然后以<code>text/json</code>的格式返回即可。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>这波是白嫖党的胜利！</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"前端部分\"><a href=\"#前端部分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前端部分\"></a>前端部分</h1><p>首先创建一个vite的项目，引入<code>tailwindcss</code>，然后修改一些配置。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221000416633.png\" alt=\"image-20221221000416633\"></p>\n<p><code>tailwindcss</code>的安装如下，安装后会出现<code>tailwind.config.cjs</code>配置文件。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yarn add tailwindcss@latest autoprefixer@latest\nnpx tailwindcss init -p</code></pre>\n\n<p>配置修改如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>删除<code>style.css</code>中的所有样式，换成<code>tailwindcss</code>即可：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改<code>tailwind</code>的配置文件，主要填搜索路径：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;** @type &#123;import(&#39;tailwindcss&#39;).Config&#125; *&#x2F;\nmodule.exports &#x3D; &#123;\n  content: [\n    &#39;.&#x2F;index.html&#39;,\n    &#39;.&#x2F;src&#x2F;**&#x2F;*.vue&#39;\n  ],\n  theme: &#123;\n    extend: &#123;&#125;,\n  &#125;,\n  plugins: [],\n&#125;</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改vite的端口号，因为本地的5173端口被占用，所以需要修改端口号。在项目根目录创建<code>vite.config.js</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">import &#123; defineConfig &#125; from &quot;vite&quot;\nimport vue from &quot;@vitejs&#x2F;plugin-vue&quot;\n\nexport default defineConfig(&#123;\n  server:&#123; host: &#39;127.0.0.1&#39;, port: 3000 &#125;,\n  plugins: [vue()],\n&#125;);</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p>接下来引入Vue，命令行输入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yarn add -D @vitejs&#x2F;plugin-vue @vue&#x2F;compiler-sfc vue@next</code></pre>\n\n<p>因为创建项目的时候没有使用Vue的模板，所以需要自己手动修改。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>创建<code>src</code>目录，再在里面创建<code>components</code>用于存放Vue组件。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将<code>main.js</code>移动到<code>src</code>下，修改为Vue的<code>main.js</code>的标准格式：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">import &#123; createApp &#125; from &#39;vue&#39;\nimport &#39;..&#x2F;style.css&#39;\nimport App from &quot;.&#x2F;App.vue&quot;\n\ncreateApp(App).mount(&quot;#app&quot;)</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改<code>index.html</code>中<code>main.js</code>的相对路径。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>src</code>下创建<code>App.vue</code>，写一个<code>Hello World</code>测试。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;template&gt;\n    &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;text-3xl bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-violet-500&quot;&gt;\n        Hello World\n    &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;template&gt;</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p>在命令行输入<code>yarn dev</code>启动开发服务器，可以看到样式引入成功。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221002613835.png\" alt=\"image-20221221002613835\"></p>\n<p>前端部分的样式编写主要就使用<code>tailwindcss</code>了。这次并没有使用Vue的组件库，因为组件库可diy的部分太少了。</p>\n<h1 id=\"后端部分\"><a href=\"#后端部分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后端部分\"></a>后端部分</h1><p>首先使用npm创建一个node项目：<code>npm init</code>。</p>\n<p>然后把以前的友链以json的格式移植过去：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221003209048.png\" alt=\"image-20221221003209048\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>本来有好多的，但是很多都访问不了了…哎，不得不感慨写博客真不一件易事。</p></blockquote>\n<p>安装<code>@vercel/node</code>和<code>typescript</code>，然后创建<code>/api/friends.ts</code>，编写如下代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-typescript\" data-language=\"typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\">import &#123; VercelRequest, VercelResponse &#125; from &#39;@vercel&#x2F;node&#39;;\nmodule.exports &#x3D; async (req: VercelRequest, res: VercelResponse) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;\n    const data &#x3D; require(&quot;..&#x2F;link.json&quot;)\n    res.setHeader(&#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;, &#39;*&#39;)\n    res.status(200).json(data);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>这部分代码做的就是读取<code>link.json</code>为对象，然后再以<code>json</code>的格式返回给前端。其中使用<code>setHeader(&#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;, &#39;*&#39;)</code>来避免跨域请求。</p>\n<p>在项目根目录创建<code>vercel.json</code>来自定义vercel的行为：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-json\" data-language=\"json\"><code class=\"language-json\">&#123;\n    &quot;routes&quot;: [\n        &#123;\n            &quot;handle&quot;: &quot;filesystem&quot;\n        &#125;,\n        &#123;\n            &quot;src&quot;: &quot;&#x2F;(.*)&quot;,\n            &quot;status&quot;: 404,\n            &quot;dest&quot;: &quot;&#x2F;index.html&quot;\n        &#125;\n    ]\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>命令行输入<code>vercel --prod</code>即可将后端部署到vercel。</p>\n<h1 id=\"前后端联调\"><a href=\"#前后端联调\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前后端联调\"></a>前后端联调</h1><p>后端部署好了，接下来前端获取api的数据然后使用<code>v-if</code>渲染出来即可。</p>\n<p>引入axios：<code>npm install axios -save</code>。</p>\n<p>axios使用get请求获取api的数据。用于这是一个异步操作，所以前面需要加上<code>await</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const friends &#x3D; await axios.get(&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog-api.fullcomb.top&#x2F;api&#x2F;friends&quot;).then(res&#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    return res.data\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n\n<p>最后将前端部署到vercel：<code>vercel --prod</code>，然后配置域名即可。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>评论区使用以前的twikoo就能实现，所以没有专门写评论区，直接将twikoo挂载到一个结点即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221004839285.png\" alt=\"image-20221221004839285\"></p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"白嫖！\"><a href=\"#白嫖！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"白嫖！\"></a>白嫖！</h1><p>这一次可谓是将白嫖做到了极致，但是同时也感受到了白嫖的代价是需要花大量的时间折腾。如果直接部署到服务器上，可能我早做完了。</p>\n<p>最后分享一个白嫖bilibili用到的字体<code>HarmonyOS</code>的方法。</p>\n<p>首先抓包查看bilibili的字体，可以发现有很多字体的文件，但是它们都有一个css父文件。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221005412003.png\" alt=\"image-20221221005412003\"></p>\n<p>访问该css文件，可以发现它为不同的<code>unicode</code>字符设置了<code>fontface</code>。这正是b站加快字体访问速度的方法。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/5/image-20221221005603720.png\" alt=\"image-20221221005603720\"></p>\n<p>我们在html中引入这个css文件后，再设置相应的<code>font-family</code>即可白嫖b站的高性能字体。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;!-- index.html --&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n    @import url(&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;s1.hdslb.com&#x2F;bfs&#x2F;static&#x2F;jinkela&#x2F;long&#x2F;font&#x2F;regular.css&quot;);\n&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">&#x2F;* style.css *&#x2F;\n* &#123;\n    font-family: HarmonyOS_Regular;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>阿b没有做防盗链我是真没想到。目前可以放心食用，坚持将白嫖进行到最后。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"rou